ORG $20088
POIN PrepsBGPal

//Status bg
ORG $88638
POIN StatusBG

ORG $88640
POIN StatusBGPal

ORG $88644
POIN StatusBGTSA

POP

ALIGN 4
PrepsBG:
#incext Png2Dmp --lz77 "PrepsBG.png" 
ALIGN 4
PrepsBGPal:
